Question 1:

篩選出屬於日本市場的使用者，針對購買金額進行獨立樣本 t 檢定。請問：實驗組的購買金額有沒有顯著高於對照組的購買金額？ 反之，針對購買金額進行獨立樣本 t 檢定，對照組金額有沒有顯著高於實驗組金額？ 請利用 ggplot2 繪製實驗組與對照組購買金額機率密度圖 (density plot)。

jp_users <- all_table %>%
    filter(country =='JP')

  • T -test for significance level : p-value = 1
t.test(jp_users[jp_users$test==1,]$purchase_amount,
       jp_users[jp_users$test==0,]$purchase_amount,
       alternative = 'greater')
## 
##  Welch Two Sample t-test
## 
## data:  jp_users[jp_users$test == 1, ]$purchase_amount and jp_users[jp_users$test == 0, ]$purchase_amount
## t = -63.113, df = 9953.1, p-value = 1
## alternative hypothesis: true difference in means is greater than 0
## 95 percent confidence interval:
##  -9.297706       Inf
## sample estimates:
## mean of x mean of y 
##  34.50391  43.56543
  • ggplot for purchase amount density plot
ggplot(jp_users, aes(purchase_amount, fill = test)) +
    geom_density(alpha = 0.3) +
    ggtitle("JP Density Plot of Purchase Amount - Test versus control:") +
    theme_bw()

Question 2:

建立購物金額與是否為實驗組、設備、性別與服務的變異數分析(ANOVA)模型。請問，模型中有哪些因子是顯著的？ - 請利用 ggplot2 繪製購買金額對應不同服務的盒狀圖 (boxplot)。 - 請進行 Tukey 事後檢定，了解 test 對於購買金額的影響，並繪製信賴區間圖形。 - 請進行 Tukey 事後檢定，了解 device 對於購買金額的影響，並繪製信賴區間圖形。

  • Based on the result, test, device and service are sinigicant factors
aov_model <- aov(
    purchase_amount ~ test + device + gender + service, all_table
)

summary(aov_model)
##                Df   Sum Sq Mean Sq   F value Pr(>F)    
## test            1  1304220 1304220 11882.853 <2e-16 ***
## device          2   463996  231998  2113.752 <2e-16 ***
## gender          1      103     103     0.942  0.332    
## service         2  1376036  688018  6268.585 <2e-16 ***
## Residuals   99993 10974881     110                     
## ---
## Signif. codes:  0 '***' 0.001 '**' 0.01 '*' 0.05 '.' 0.1 ' ' 1
  • ggplot: service type
ggplot(all_table, aes(x = service, y= purchase_amount)) +
    geom_boxplot() +
    theme_bw()

  • Tukey 事後檢定，了解 test 對於購買金額的影響，並繪製信賴區間圖形。
TukeyHSD(aov_model, 'test')
##   Tukey multiple comparisons of means
##     95% family-wise confidence level
## 
## Fit: aov(formula = purchase_amount ~ test + device + gender + service, data = all_table)
## 
## $test
##         diff      lwr      upr p adj
## 1-0 7.222798 7.092933 7.352663     0
plot(TukeyHSD(aov_model,'test'))

  • Tukey 事後檢定，了解 device 對於購買金額的影響，並繪製信賴區間圖形。
TukeyHSD(aov_model, 'device')
##   Tukey multiple comparisons of means
##     95% family-wise confidence level
## 
## Fit: aov(formula = purchase_amount ~ test + device + gender + service, data = all_table)
## 
## $device
##                          diff       lwr       upr p adj
## ios_app-android_app  5.881650  5.669637  6.093662     0
## pc_web-android_app   3.913586  3.701622  4.125549     0
## pc_web-ios_app      -1.968064 -2.141917 -1.794211     0
plot(TukeyHSD(aov_model,'device'))

Note that the echo = FALSE parameter was added to the code chunk to prevent printing of the R code that generated the plot.
